column6: Kuoni is a tourist travel company. Kuoni was founded in 1906 and is currently headquartered in Zurich, Switzerland.

Thomas Cook Group plc, through its subsidiaries, provided leisure travel services in the UK and internationally. The company also engaged in the airline, hotel, tour operation, and travel agency activities, as well as offering foreign exchange and travel assurance services. The company was founded in 1841 and was based in London, UK. In September 2019, the company went into compulsory liquidation.
